                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13081549" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 9 Aug 2011 10:00:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If using 0 as timeout on pollEnrich with a scheduled polling consumer (using EventDrivenPollingConsumer to poll) then Camel now ensures there is given time for at least one scheduled poll run. Otherwise the scheduler would not be able to poll within a 0 timeout&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13095886" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 2 Sep 2011 09:25:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Cannot backport to 2.8.1 as it has API changes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
